[src:secure-boot-measured/unified-extensible-firmware-interface] During 2005, more than one million Intel systems shipped with Intel's implementation of UEFI.
[src:secure-boot-measured/unified-extensible-firmware-interface] New mobile, desktop and server products, using Intel's implementation of UEFI, started shipping in 2006.
